50|$|Between 4-8 August {{a further}} series of large eruptions {{destroyed}} approximately 80% of the town, burying it under 1.4 m of ash. This <b>hot</b> <b>material</b> burned {{many of the}} buildings, making habitation nearly impossible {{for many of the}} residents.|$|E
